      <bioghist id="aspace_ef05e2a32e7f7158676f6ac5181fd0d3">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Treasury Services at Yale is the office responsible for valuing, acknowledging, and processing gifts to Yale; maintaining copies of all agreements, deeds, wills, and trusts; and administering property and casualty insurance and faculty mortgages and emergency loans.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_5dcd42baec4d1a3ec03793d61fb14bf2">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of estates, wills, and trusts maintained by Yale Treasury Services.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
